# BoldTake — Prediction-Based Sports Game Using Virtual Credits

**Student:** Dhruv Dhola (20001467)
**Module:** B8IS133 PROJECT — BSc (Hons) in Computing
**Repo:** https://github.com/dhruvd275/prediction-game-platform

---

## Overview

BoldTake is a web-based sports prediction game where users sign up, receive virtual credits, and use them to predict outcomes of real sports events across Formula 1, Cricket, and Football. No real money is involved — it is fully simulated and academic.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Backend | Node.js + Express |
| Database | PostgreSQL 16 (Docker) |
| Auth | JWT + bcrypt |
| Frontend | Ionic + Angular |
| Version Control | Git + GitHub |

---

