## Database Commands

### Connect to Database

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game
```

### View All Tables

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "\dt"
```

### View All Users

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT id, email, username, credits FROM users ORDER BY id;"
```

### View All Events

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT id, sport, name, starts_at FROM events ORDER BY id;"
```

### View All Markets

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT id, event_id, type, status, cutoff_at FROM markets ORDER BY id;"
```

### View All Predictions

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT id, user_id, market_id, selection, stake, status FROM predictions ORDER BY id;"
```

### View Credit Log

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT * FROM credit_log ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 20;"
```

### View Leaderboard

```bash
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT username, credits FROM users ORDER BY credits DESC;"
```

